observer (1.0.3) testing; urgency=medium

  * Add a system tray icon with wake, statistics/history, and quit actions.
  * Wake the prompt from a tray left-click in addition to Win+Alt+G.
  * Add per-user single-instance detection; a second launch wakes the running
    instance, prints a warning, and exits.
  * Add Win+Alt+H as an X11 global shortcut for opening statistics/history
    while waiting.
  * Add -c/--cancel to configure how many consecutive prompt cancels exit the
    app.
  * Expand README statistics/history documentation to cover calendar summaries,
    charts, sortable record tables, and navigation shortcuts.

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Mon, 15 Jun 2026 10:30:00 +0800

observer (1.0.2) testing; urgency=medium

  * Fix statistics toolbar view switching by using check tools with manual
    exclusivity, so Calendar and Day/Week/Month/Year stay one logical group
    across the separator.
  * Fix toolbar shortcut help for view buttons by passing wxNullBitmap before
    shortHelp in AddCheckTool.
  * Redesign the statistics calendar cells with Gregorian dates top-left, lunar
    labels beneath them, and record counts with colour dots bottom-right.
  * Paint calendar fills first and draw grid lines afterward as a separate line
    set, keeping 1px borders consistent and omitting lines around empty cells.
  * Highlight today with an orange fill and border, and show adjacent month
    names in the calendar header navigation.
  * Switch the statistics record table to wxGenericListCtrl for reliable
    sorting and dark-theme rendering.
  * Record empty submissions and store both prompt and submit timestamps,
    including prompt duration in directory logs and SQLite rows.
  * Add a Ctrl-H modal statistics dialog with calendar, day, week, month, and
    year analysis views.
  * Add a custom calendar with lunar day labels, holiday highlighting, selected
    day summaries, record markers, and sortable record tables.
  * Add --weekstart to choose Monday or Sunday as the calendar week start.
  * Improve statistics navigation with toolbar actions and keyboard shortcuts.

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Sun, 14 Jun 2026 17:45:00 +0800

observer (1.0.1) testing; urgency=medium

  * Add locale selection with -l/--locale and load development translations
    relative to the executable path.
  * Add prompt Quit footer action and Ctrl-Q as an in-prompt quit shortcut.
  * Add a Win+Alt+G X11 global hotkey for immediate prompts while waiting.
  * Add --opacity to control final prompt opacity from 0 to 100 percent.
  * Add the X11 build dependency required by the global hotkey implementation.

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Sat, 13 Jun 2026 22:05:05 +0800

observer (1.0.0) testing; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of the oremind desktop self-observation reminder.
  * Add wxWidgets background app flow with immediate startup prompt, timer-based
    reminders, snooze handling, and three-Escape exit behavior.
  * Add dark/light prompt themes, quote canvas, emoji score controls, keyboard
    shortcuts, interval editing, and slide/fade prompt transitions.
  * Add SQLite storage by default under ~/.observer/observer.sqlite3 and
    directory-based daily text logs through --sqlite-db.
  * Trim activity text, skip empty submissions, and omit default e/m/g scores
    from persisted records.
  * Add gettext catalogs, bash completion, manpage, and project documentation.
 
 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Sat, 13 Jun 2026 19:54:27 +0800
